   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
    There are a couple of different 
ways to sign "breakfast."
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    1.  A popular sign for 
"breakfast" is a combination of "EAT and
  MORNING."
    <br/>
    <br/>
    BREAKFAST:
    <br/>
